# Projecting Kotlin: Core Technology Stack

- **Language:** Kotlin
- **UI:** Jetpack Compose (Material 3)
- **Architecture:** Clean Architecture (Multi-module), MVVM (Refer to [architecture.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/architecture.mdc))
- **Async:** Kotlin Coroutines & Flow
- **Navigation:** Jetpack Navigation Compose (Refer to @project-structure.mdc for `:navigation` module)
- **DI:** Hilt (Refer to [architecture.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/architecture.mdc))
- **Backend/DB:**
  - Firebase Firestore: Main NoSQL data storage (Refer to [firestore-schema.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/firestore-schema.mdc))
  - Firebase Authentication: User auth.
  - Firebase Storage: File storage.
  - Retrofit & OkHttp (Planned): External API communication.
- **Local DB:** Room (Uses KSP).
- **Code Generation:** KSP (Hilt, Room).
- **Logging:** Sentry (Refer to [project-structure.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/project-structure.mdc) for `:core:core_logging` Sodule).



